Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
models.Inventory
public class Inventory extends Object
The Inventory class represents an item in the inventory system. It holds details about the item's ID, name, quantity in stock, unit of measurement, reorder threshold, and price per unit. This class provides getter and setter methods to access and modify the inventory details. It also overrides the toString() method to provide a string representation of the inventory item.
